==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unfeigned
<hw>Un*feigned"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not feigned; not
counterfeit; not hypocritical; real; sincere; genuine; <as>as,
<ex>unfeigned</ex> piety; <ex>unfeigned</ex> love to man</as>.</def>
⟦ldquo⟧Good faith <xex>unfeigned</xex>.⟦rdquo⟧ <au>Chaucer.</au> --
<wordforms><wf>Un*feign"ed*ly</wf> <pr>(#)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Un*feign"ed*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unfellow</ent>⟦br⟧
